 页所描述的，原本哆啦 A 梦的名字全都是用片假名书写的（ドラエモン），但是在工厂生产完了，进行机器人登记的时候，哆啦 A 梦写完名字的前部分ドラ后，想不起来后半部分的片假名エモン怎么写了（果然是不良品啊 (-_-;)），只好写平假名えもん。于是哆啦 A 梦的名字就一半片假名一半平假名了。 汉语版「哆啦 A 梦」的译名，采用一半汉字一半字母，实际上是非常忠实地反映了这个设定的 这个解释似乎在正剧外？而且我觉得如果要翻过来的话，不良品的叮当「用错同音字」更靠谱，比如「卫门」写成「为萌」，而不是用了英文。所以我问题更多的是想知道这么差的译名是如何拍板的…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-411332a50ab63895c56d1c6d98bebce2.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/30836738"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I3qjFj+2M56MTEAMaBzQ1MTcwMzcgqIusqwUwFTj/A0ApcggzMDgzNjczOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1622524495.5584939", "card_id": "Q_462118314", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 255}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "618 的 iPhone 12 降到 4800 多，现在值得入手吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "这波降价幅度有点心动，现在是最便宜的吗，要不要等到 6 月 18 号？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-09515c0115e0868d59973016d864f998_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/462118314"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3qjFj+2M56MTEAMaCDY0OTcyNDA0ILm6yYUGMCE4hAdAKnIJNDYyMTE4MzE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1622524495.5589783", "card_id": "Q_447643338", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 118}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么青梅竹马的甜甜小说吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最好是一直甜甜的哦"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9cf3226b773deec9c83c7e3dce0d6172_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447643338"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3qjFj+2M56MTEAMaCDYxNzU1MDMzIK/3g4IGMAE40gZAK3IJNDQ3NjQzMzM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmT